<div>
	<h2 id="d1">1.全局阿尔法值：</h2>
	<pre>
		oGC.globalAlpha=0.5;  //效果：半透明
	</pre>
</div>
<div>
	<h2 id="d2">2.全局混合选项：</h2>
	<pre>
		oGC.globalCompositeOperation="";  //多图片不同的混合效果
		取值：
			1. source-over  //默认
			<img src="images/5_01.png"/>
			2. destination-over
			<img src="images/5_02.png"/>
			3. source-atop
			<img src="images/5_03.png"/>
			4. destination-atop
			<img src="images/5_04.png"/>
			5. source-in
			<img src="images/5_05.png"/>
			6. destination-in
			<img src="images/5_06.png"/>
			7. destination-out
			<img src="images/5_07.png"/>
			8. source-out
			<img src="images/5_08.png"/>
			9. lighter
			<img src="images/5_09.png"/>
			10. copy
