<div>
	<h2 id="d4">4.导出图片：</h2>
	<pre>
		火狐浏览器-> 右键鼠标 ->将图像另存为
	</pre>
</div>

<div>
	<h2 id="d5">5.判断某一个坐标点时候在某个区域内：</h2>
	<pre>
		语法：canvasContext.isPointInPath(x,y)

		实例：
		window.onload=function(){
			var huabu=document.getElementById("c1");
			var canvasContext=huabu.getContext("2d");
			/*画一个黑色实心圆*/
			canvasContext.beginPath();
			canvasContext.arc(200,200,50,0,360*Math.PI*180,false);
			canvasContext.closePath();
			canvasContext.fill();
			/*当按下鼠标左键时判断此时的坐标是否在黑色实心圆范围之内*/
			huabu.onmousedown=function(ev){
				var ev=ev;
				var x=ev.clientX-huabu.offsetLeft;
				var y=ev.clientY-huabu.offsetTop;
				if(canvasContext.isPointInPath(x,y)){
					alert("123");
				}
			}
		}
	</pre>
</div>

	


</div>
</div>
